    "biography": "<p>A lightning-fast Awakened mongoose (Herpestes illustris) and consummate snake-killer that dances its prey into a stupor before the kill.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Accident (Zone), Enhanced Movement, Hypnotic Dance (as Hypnotic Song except range; affects snakes and creatures under 1 m), Immunity to Poisons (wholly immune to snake venom)</p><p><strong>Weaknesses:</strong> Dietary Requirement (snakes — venom and hepatic enzymes)</p><p><em>Attacks: 3L, Reach −1 (bite). Habitat: Scrub and open woodland. Range: Spain, Portugal, southern France, Sicily, Sardinia, southern Italy. Vs a hypnotized snake the bite is 5D; vs any other hypnotized target 6S. 3D6 Initiative dice. Book Intelligence 2/5. PAE p.85.</em></p>",
